Privacy Policy: TruckXpress: Cargo Delivery Challenge
TruckXpress: Cargo Delivery Challenge game. This Privacy Policy is designed to inform you about our practices regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of information that you may provide through our app.
Information We Collect
When you use our app, we may collect both personal and non-personal information from you. This may include your name, email address, device ID, IP address, in-game activity, and purchases.
How We Collect Information
We collect information when you create an account, interact with our app, make in-app purchases, and choose to share data through our app.
Use of Collected Information
We may use the information we collect to enhance your gaming experience, improve our services, provide customer support, and send you information about our products and services.
Information Sharing
We do not rent or sell your personal information to third parties. However, we may share information with third-party service providers under strict confidentiality agreements. We may also be required to disclose your personal information if mandated by law.
Data Protection
We have implemented robust security measures to protect your information from unauthorized access and misuse. These measures include encryption technologies and secure server infrastructure.
User Rights
You have the right to access, modify, amend, or delete your personal information at any time, subject to local laws and regulations.
Children's Privacy
Our application is not intended for users under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect or store personal information from children under 13 years of age.
Changes to the Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy periodically. When we make changes to the policy, we will notify you by publishing the revised Privacy Policy on this page. Additionally, we will update the "Last updated" date at the top of the policy content for your convenience.
Contact Information
If you have any concerns or queries regarding our Privacy Policy, please contact us via [Your Contact Information].
